Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Be yourself, they say, but be assertive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:27.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hold your ground but do not be unkind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:32.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I have sought to be both lamb and lion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:37.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Heartache is the thing I tend to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can I only have what I can capture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:48.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Will I be unheard~ unless I shout
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Clamor overwhelms~~ me and I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:58.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What is there to be so~ loud about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:03.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Many are the mu~sings of my shy~~~~~ heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:06.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Though precious few are spoken out aloud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:13.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How I wish to wrap them up in confidence and style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:17.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And send them out like magic through the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:23.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then everyone would listen and I wouldn't be afraid~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:27.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't shrink away~~ and disappear~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:32.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't want them to worship me or care that much at all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:37.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I only want to know~ they know~~ I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:43.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I can wear a mask of pluck and power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But it never says what I intend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:54.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Words become like scissors in my keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:58.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And friendships are so difficult to mend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:03.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't want to shout above the babble
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure~ what I would say
